595
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:05,560
She said she had something to do

596
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:06,520
and would come later.

597
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,080
Something to do?

598
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:10,630
Young Master Zhan,

599
