656
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:57,400
Lingshui.

657
00:35:58,450 --> 00:35:59,720
Let's return to the city first.

658
00:35:59,720 --> 00:36:00,960
We'll go to Lingshui tomorrow.

659
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:01,800
No need to return.

660
00:36:02,030 --> 00:36:03,110
I've packed everything

661
00:36:03,110 --> 00:36:04,030
we need for the road.

662
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:05,080
We can set off now.

663
00:36:08,510 --> 00:36:10,080
A fortune-teller back then

664
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,660
once said I was an unlucky child.

665
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,080
So, my father

666
00:36:13,230 --> 00:36:14,440
sent me far away.

667
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:16,230
If the weak

668
00:36:16,360 --> 00:36:17,710
are unjustly blamed for everything

669
00:36:17,710 --> 00:36:19,150
by the world,

670
00:36:19,710 --> 00:36:20,760
and they neither inquire

671
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:21,790
nor resist,

672
00:36:22,110 --> 00:36:23,190
doesn't that make them

673
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,400
accomplices

674
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,000
to these villains' lies?

675
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,230
If I've been falsely accused,

676
00:36:28,510 --> 00:36:30,150
I'll make sure the accusers

677
00:36:30,510 --> 00:36:31,360
pay the price.

678
00:36:36,230 --> 00:36:37,070
Chief.

679
00:36:37,550 --> 00:36:38,390
Chief?

680
00:36:45,030 --> 00:36:46,280
Chief, were you just

681
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,590
worried about Miss Si?

682
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:49,670
I'm not sure

683
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:50,880
if I should say this,

684
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,110
but I really fear Miss Si

685
00:36:53,110 --> 00:36:54,560
has already been using you.

686
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,040
Chief, I haven't finished.

687
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,710
I haven't started my analysis.

688
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:00,510
I think Miss Si can prophesy

689
00:37:00,510 --> 00:37:02,400
like the Saintess.

690
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,240
Chief.

691
00:37:12,030 --> 00:37:12,960
Yu.

692
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:14,880
- Qi.
- Where are you going?

693
00:37:16,510 --> 00:37:19,030
I'm an Imperial Insignia Guard now,

694
00:37:19,030 --> 00:37:21,070
so we're returning to Lingshui
before I start

695
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:22,520
to pay respects to our ancestors

696
00:37:22,630 --> 00:37:24,040
and enjoy the scenery.

697
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:25,550
I've never been to Lingshui,

698
00:37:25,550 --> 00:37:26,760
so I thought I'd join the fun.

699
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,110
Your plan sounds good.

700
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:29,280
Commandant Yu,

701
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:31,000
why don't you come with us?

702
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:33,190
Yeah, the more the merrier.

703
00:37:33,190 --> 00:37:34,030
Sure.

704
00:37:34,150 --> 00:37:35,520
My chief has official duties.

705
00:37:35,710 --> 00:37:36,550
Official duties?

706
00:37:37,150 --> 00:37:38,150
I thought you were here

707
00:37:38,150 --> 00:37:39,630
to send us off.

708
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:41,190
That's not totally true.

709
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,280
We were just...

710
00:37:42,280 --> 00:37:44,790
We were just wandering around nearby

711
00:37:45,230 --> 00:37:46,590
without a destination in mind.

712
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:48,630
Why don't we join you

713
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,320
for some sightseeing?

714
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:51,270
That sounds great.

715
00:37:51,710 --> 00:37:52,550
Yu,

716
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:54,040
they're riding too slowly.

717
00:37:54,050 --> 00:37:55,560
I was just thinking of finding someone

718
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:56,350
to race horses with.

719
00:37:56,380 --> 00:37:57,980
You want to race horses with Qi?

720
00:37:57,980 --> 00:37:58,920
Catch up with me first.

721
00:37:59,380 --> 00:38:00,480
Without a starting signal?

722
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:01,510
You two go ahead.

723
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:02,550
I need to catch my breath.

724
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:03,590
Alright, keep up.

725
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:21,120
What's wrong?

726
00:38:21,960 --> 00:38:22,800
Are you missing home?

727
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,200
It's nothing.

728
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:36,360
I'm glad you're here.

729
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:13,870
Miss Jiang,

730
00:39:14,430 --> 00:39:15,480
the scenery is beautiful.

731
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,550
Why not take a walk?

732
00:39:16,550 --> 00:39:17,520
Thank you, Commandant Yu.

733
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:18,840
It's fine.

734
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:20,480
I'll just sit here and enjoy the view.

735
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:22,840
This isn't a court.

736
00:39:23,110 --> 00:39:24,850
Don't call me Commandant.
It's too formal.

737
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:28,440
Shall I call you

738
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:29,800
Mr. Yu?

739
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:30,950
Sure.

740
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:32,760
Mr. Yu,

741
00:39:34,230 --> 00:39:36,040
thank you

742
00:39:36,510 --> 00:39:37,670
for helping my brother.

743
00:39:37,970 --> 00:39:39,720
Neighbors are better
than distant relatives.

744
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:41,030
If there's anything

745
00:39:41,030 --> 00:39:42,400
you need help with in the future,

746
00:39:42,510 --> 00:39:43,250
just let me know.

747
00:39:43,300 --> 00:39:44,790
Is it really just a neighborly thing?

748
00:39:44,830 --> 00:39:46,650
There are at least seven
or eight households

749
00:39:46,650 --> 00:39:48,100
living in our neighborhood,

750
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,400
but I've never seen Mr. Yu

751
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:51,150
put so much effort into other people.

752
00:39:51,280 --> 00:39:52,590
Miss, it's because of you.

753
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:53,980
You're being talkative.

754
00:39:58,960 --> 00:39:59,800
Mr. Yu,

755
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:01,190
I had a nightmare and dreamed

756
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:02,410
my brother would be in danger,

757
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:04,190
but when I told others,

758
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:05,960
they all thought I was overreacting.

759
00:40:06,590 --> 00:40:08,150
Only you

760
