762
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,360
But it is quite amazing

763
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,560
when dreams come true.

764
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:19,230
Have you ever dreamed of anything else?

765
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:20,880
Maybe you can foresee the future.

766
00:40:25,590 --> 00:40:27,000
Mr. Yu, you're just joking.

767
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,300
How could an ordinary person

768
00:40:28,300 --> 00:40:29,270
have such an ability?

769
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,440
Yu, Si,

770
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:41,150
there's a beautiful stream ahead.

771
00:40:41,150 --> 00:40:42,660
Shall we go and rest there for a while?

772
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:43,720
I caught it!

773
00:40:44,150 --> 00:40:45,520
Long Dan, you're amazing!

774
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:47,400
Chief, I caught it!

775
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,630
Hurry and put it here.

776
00:40:48,630 --> 00:40:50,230
- So impressive!
- What a big fish!

777
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:51,190
Hurry! It's so slippery!

778
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:53,670
Isn't it too small?

779
00:40:55,110 --> 00:40:56,520
