780
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:57,720
Come on.

781
00:40:58,840 --> 00:41:00,140
Young Master Zhan, can you do it?

782
00:41:13,590 --> 00:41:15,110
Zhan, you go start the fire.

783
00:41:16,030 --> 00:41:17,270
I'll go start the fire instead.

784
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:36,000
There's no firewood.

785
00:41:37,150 --> 00:41:38,040
I'll help you.

786
00:41:38,720 --> 00:41:40,460
I'll go find some dry firewood
over there.

787
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:41,880
Alright.

788
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:43,480
Don't cut yourself.

789
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:59,550
Jiang Zhan, look! I caught one!

790
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:00,440
So impressive!

